b2283f9528607aaa30","tid":397191,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:07:12.000Z","msg":"美欺夠膽就同我挑lf2"},{"pid":"41ab21e36386382ddc0725301aa37d9ef4d2d3bb","tid":397191,"uid":65587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:08:26.000Z","msg":"SiuMa世界第一"},{"pid":"85db9fa39e031cf963c63e64e518b249cb178c9c","tid":397191,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:10:12.000Z","msg":"你話過黎就過黎，你乜水呀？😑"},{"pid":"d1045003481488ad836df4d9d46a2be0762913bf","tid":397191,"uid":101464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:33:22.000Z","msg":"好尷尬"},{"pid":"48f71de2287229aa0d5e4f8d7cf0204743802d35","tid":397191,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:39:27.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"},{"pid":"5eeba082aea1b8c806e28048ca383d4d5524a01d","tid":397191,"uid":31475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:42:29.000Z","msg":"樓主認真on9<br />\n睇到都覺得掉架"},{"pid":"6e2456adb5020ed5ea7f12292ac48681973e99cd","tid":397191,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美斯：我上次咪黎左香港挑贏曬成隊港隊囉，你挑贏左港隊再call我啦</blockquote><br />\n玩過鬥獸棋未先</blockquote><br />\n你係貓黎咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c44cdf8a797366614ce83a95ecfab5cead79c2","tid":397191,"uid":24252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T13:05:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3lxV_SYZqDQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3lxV_SYZqDQ&d=%2Foq5WVFsgko3n0FKNOjHdYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=03374ac1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3lxV_SYZqDQ</a>"}]}